  "id": "69fb32c86a1d7eed64aa427f",
  "title": "デライトや Cosense に足りないのはぶっちゃけキムタク理論",
  "created": 1778070221,
  "updated": 1778135368,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69fb32c86a1d7eed64aa427f",
      "text": "デライトや Cosense に足りないのはぶっちゃけキムタク理論",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070221,
      "updated": 1778070257
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb32b9000000000076223a",
      "text": "略して[デコキム]理論",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
      "created": 1778070221,
      "updated": 1778135368
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb334b000000000076223c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070366,
      "updated": 1778070366
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb334e000000000076223e",
      "text": " [デライト]も[Cosense]も十分な実装水準にある",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070369,
      "updated": 1778070396
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb339e0000000000762242",
      "text": " 素晴らしさもある",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070449,
      "updated": 1778070454
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb3369000000000076223f",
      "text": " 歴史もある",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070396,
      "updated": 1778070413
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb337a0000000000762240",
      "text": " コミュニティもある",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070413,
      "updated": 1778070416
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb337d0000000000762241",
      "text": " だが理性だけに訴えていてはいつまで経ってもマイナーサービスの域を出ないだろう",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070417,
      "updated": 1778070442
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb334b000000000076223d",
      "text": " 大衆の心を掴むには感性に訴える何かが必要",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070366,
      "updated": 1778070488
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb355c0000000000762245",
      "text": " Cosense にキムタクがいたらどうか",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070895,
      "updated": 1778070902
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb35a00000000000762246",
      "text": "  あっという間に世間に広がるだろう",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070963,
      "updated": 1778070977
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb33a80000000000762243",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1778070459,
      "updated": 1778070459
    },
    {
      "id": "69fb32bb000000000076223b",
      "text": "[デライト.icon] [cosense.icon]",
      "userId": "686b72ebdffe36b729b4453d",
